name: Decorative Item Octave
description: New to the collection, the Octave tray combines the contrasts of two materials: wenge, a wood essence with an irregular and textured grain, and lacquer, shiny, perfectly smooth and stretched. Thought out in generous proportions, Octave is designed to support the different uses of a contemporary art of living. Its wenge handles give it a strong personality, balanced by lines softened by subtle details.
